This patch fixes TAHI test case nd/74. 
Redirects to routers for which no valid neighbor cache entry existed
were ignored (#38554).

--- linux-2.6.5/net/ipv6/route.c.tahi	2004-05-11 11:01:03.000000000 +0200
+++ linux-2.6.5/net/ipv6/route.c	2004-05-11 11:04:06.000000000 +0200
@@ -1036,6 +1036,7 @@
